Major changes from version 0.1 to 0.2:

- Improve 3D view navigation
- Allow saving isosurfaces
- Add experimental support for showing isosurfaces with OSVR (not in binary packages)
- Add support for 3D input devices under Linux
- Allow loaders to be written as external programs
- Add support for loading VGI files
- Rework the side panel in the UI
- Generally improve performance and error handling
